author: mxmanghi
msg: * tests/upload.[rvt|test]: fix upload message sent to server. The end boundary
went undetected and Rivet added it to the uploaded file. Thus the problem
affected only the test, not the module. Added delimiter to the returned
message to allow easy spotting of an empty string.

author: hwright
msg: Remove a temporary API.  This also allows reverting an added directory which is
the CWD.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/wc.h
(svn_wc__temp_get_relpath): Remove.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/adm_ops.c
(revert_entry): Don't use the API, and in the process, allow a revert of
an added directory if it is the CWD.
(revert_internal): Remove an unused path, and superflous call to the
temp API.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(make_editor): Use the anchor_abspath in place of the relpath, and remove
a call to the temp API.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/lock.c
(svn_wc__temp_get_relpath): Remove.
